Class ColumnParent

public class ColumnParent
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.apache.thrift.TBase<ColumnParent,ColumnParent._Fields>, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

ColumnParent is used when selecting groups of columns from the same ColumnFamily. In directory structure terms, imagine ColumnParent as ColumnPath + '/../'. See also ColumnPath
